episodes.title: Exclusive Clip From Cult-Focused Docuseries "THE FOURTH WALL"
episodes.description:
THE FOURTH WALL is a character-driven documentary series in which the son of cult leaders investigates the transgressive group he was raised inside of, discovering long-buried secrets about the truth of his childhood. This is the story of the Sullivanians, New York’s secretive “psychotherapy sex cult,” which was hidden in plain sight on Manhattan's Upper West Side in the 1970s and ’80s, thriving underground from its utopian heyday to its dramatic collapse in 1991. 

The Fourth Wall premiered at Tribeca Film Festival and is currently looking for distribution.
